pt.ist.fenixframework.consistencyPredicates

Class ConsistencyPredicateSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.ist.fenixframework.consistencyPredicates.ConsistencyPredicateSystem

  • public class ConsistencyPredicateSystem
extends Object
    This class contains the old JVSTM code to determine which consistency predicates affect which domain classes. This class is used by the framework only when it is NOT allowed to create DomainMetaObjects. Otherwise, the DomainMetaClass should be used under normal circumstances.
